    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your<strong> garlic </strong>and add it to a <strong>food processor</strong> with <strong>half</strong> your<strong> cherry tomatoes </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), your <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong>,<strong> agave</strong>,<strong> red wine vinegar</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and smooth – this is your <strong>sun-dried tomato dressing</strong></p>",
