    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>remaining cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways and remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a teaspoon</p><p>Peel away the skin, then cut in half again – these are your<strong> avocado quarters</strong></p>",
