    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>dried chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>on a plate – this is your <strong>sesame chilli mix</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>avocado quarters </strong>to the <strong>sesame chilli mix </strong>and press gently until well coated – this is your <strong>sesame chilli avo</strong></p><p>Reserve any <strong>remaining sesame chilli mix</strong></p>",
