    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Combine the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and <strong>bean mix </strong>in a large bowl with the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes </strong>and the <strong>sun-dried tomato dressing</strong></p><p>Give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>sun-dried tomato bean salad</strong></p>",
